  "description": "<i>Civil Service - II</i> is a fantasy text adventure and is the sequel to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/civil-service\">The Civil Service</a>.<br><br>The premise of this game is the same as its predecessor i.e. that the Civil Service is to be privatised and reorganised and as a result all recruits must go through a tough interview process designed to test puzzle solving skills and lateral thinking. There are no gems to collect this time and the player does not start the game naked.<br><br>This game was developed using <i>Professional Adventure Writer</i>. It supports the standard shortcuts such as N/S/E/W for North/South/East/West as well as more advanced commands, however to make the game more of a challenge the RAMSAVE command has been disabled",
